status: implemented-deploy-held
summary: Wave 10 implemented the first schema-free incident/escalation lifecycle slice from the E2E orchestration plan Wave 3. No real operational data was imported, no production DB rows were created/updated/deleted, and no production deploy was performed because required browser/live checks are blocked in this sandbox.

