wave10_scope:
  - Added client-side conserjeria visibility filtering for incidents raised by or assigned to the conserjeria role/session metadata.
  - Added incident detail sheet with operational context and metadata-backed movement history.
  - Added lifecycle actions for supervisor/gerencia: take, resolve with required comment, reassign, send back, escalate.
  - Added conserjeria close-with-note action for raised/assigned incidents.
  - Added escalation payload source context/history so Junta and Reportes can show where escalation came from.
  - Added mocked Playwright coverage for conserjeria visibility/closure and supervisor resolution/escalation/Junta review without live Supabase writes.

